body:
Features: * Improves compatibility with KDE Plasma 6.5 (#2093, Display) * Adds a `tempSensor` option to specify the sensor name used for CPU temperature detection (CPU) * Example: `{ "type": "cpu", "tempSensor": "hwmon0" /* Use /sys/class/hwmon/hwmon0 for temperature detection */ }` * Refines Memory usage detection on macOS to match Activity Monitor more closely (Memory, macOS) * Minor optimizations Bugfixes: * Fixes cache line size detection (CPU, macOS) Logos: * Removes Opak * Updates GXDE ---
